{"tid":1353141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"727驚俾人一鋪清？你去邊都會一鋪清架啦","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:04:59.000Z","uid":90601,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46bbd342e8ebf90d1cfda59ebe7ce374437ac98d","tid":1353141,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"今時今日<br />\n仲以為政府會同你劃地而治？<br />\n你估下次港島行動，就唔會有黑幫？？<br />\n<br />\n政府高調用鄉黑打人<br />\n就係想你地驚，無人再抗爭<br />\n依家和理非都未出聲話驚，反而驚勇武會俾人剿？<br />\n果日中外媒體都會入去影實，你同我講驚人俾人打？<br />\n<br />\n727就去撚硬、將會以和平遊行主題進行<br />\n但若果有人被武力對待，抗爭者將會作出「適當防衛」<br />\n<br />\n唔好退縮啦大家<br />\n死左六個人，幾十人流亡緊啦"},{"pid":"d17e092ce13c9fe9740d0df1a1e221c82d97b4c2","tid":1353141,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"285235744cd258a2167c9f9f32a04706918b87c6","tid":1353141,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8f2f86b2032ce8a618babadba6971302dbdaed3","tid":1353141,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727統一口徑</span>"},{"pid":"4babd84a399794cda8d5f214bcd9a8bc0403829a","tid":1353141,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"Diu"},{"pid":"e15033fc4e9212c23c3b1961f03dc82ce08772f1","tid":1353141,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"咪撚係<br />\n<br />\n你咪清晒啲勇武囉<br />\n<br />\n睇下民怨會幾大"},{"pid":"63def8b1f84e39d05c0efa4d274fcc1d35d6c8cf","tid":1353141,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b66b8fca0f2a779aa624129ad3320152a90749d6","tid":1353141,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"我想問727入到去D黑社會匿埋哂或者返哂上深圳揼骨咁點? <br />\n<br />\n到時入到村又佢地又搵成班亞婆亞伯係到喊哂口對住咁點處理 (參考: